## Events

- **site_config_changed**: Generic config change (includes all flags)
- **stream_global_status**: Streaming enabled/disabled globally
- **chat_global_status**: Chat enabled/disabled globally
- **comments_global_status**: Comments enabled/disabled globally
- **webhooks_global_status**: Webhooks enabled/disabled globally

## Use Cases

1. **Disable UI features**: If streaming is disabled, don't show stream controls
